Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.27,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康妙风体W2\fs80\fsp-20\bord0\1c&H374948&\pos(304,118)}女高中生去做采访了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.27,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康妙风体W2\fs60\fsp-30\bord0\1c&H374948&\pos(784,406)}每个人十分钟左右\N请把工作内容\N告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该去采访了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好 你真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是直播 还可以重来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有说过海浪会越来越凶猛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把握好时间 人家说后面还会我们帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不叫醒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不狠狠地叫 我醒不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下等一下 再给我30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不对 15分钟就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们在外面等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她没有眉毛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多女生都会修掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那才比较普通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们往南走的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会在海上几处称为「站点」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收集微生物和海水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为此船上搭载了不少有用的器材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是采水器和温盐深仪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 这就是…采水器…和温盐深仪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:30.77,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}采集这类矿石的同时 要调查南极的地质情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}移开点 移开点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麦克风太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.47,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}调查地底数公里的地质层
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.18,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来研究远古时期地球的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人倒是留着眉毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你听人家说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了糟了糟了 迟到了迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该往哪边走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:53.24,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康布丁体W7\fs25\bord1\1c&H3C4041&\3c&H4D5F63&\pos(316,276)}女高中生的房间{\i1}！！{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:53.24,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康布丁体W7\fs25\bord1\1c&H3C4041&\3c&H4D5F63&\pos(352,444)}进门前先{\fn华康POP1体W7\1c&H48E8E4&}敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯嗯 等你们好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里也能做甜点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然只是用手头的材料做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就麻烦你们处理那些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才说要带削皮器的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}铃这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有这么多没削啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过这种事做起来真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理很喜欢机械式作业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们四个加起来才刚过一马力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很慢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正知道你们在家不帮家务啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过慢就慢点 别急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别伤到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我毕竟是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是职业厨师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}平时是食堂阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}常面对跟你们一样挑三拣四的顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又要考虑菜单又要下厨做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们加油 早点学会怎么搭船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么搭船？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:15.67,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天一一〇〇至一七〇〇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:18.38,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船上跑步训练 逆时针跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以在船上跑步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说 我们可以出去运动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}运动？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}削完了就带你们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}运动也算队员的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要在这里跑步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}广播里说顺时针 就是这个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说逆时针就是反方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不同的日子跑的方向不一样 要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概要跑多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这没有绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过你们也听过不少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}观测队队员比拼的就是体能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有时得在零下几十度的环境下作业一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记住这点 好好锻炼自己就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈以前也总是会运动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为体能不足而累倒 不仅是自己什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还会要旁边的人出手来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都到南极了 你们也不想当拖油瓶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 我们也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小理还没搞清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她很快就会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么…这么…大啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在这里走过很多圈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…大家都差不多这个速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人居然也能跑这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外表是个女科学家 体能却相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等…慢着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}18
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从南极回去的时候 我们要变成亚马逊女战士了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有那么容易当
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 最后一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼻头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月 难道你手抬不起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是敢做什么 我可不会放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:55.56,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康隶书体W5\1c&H3B3836&\3c&HD1DDEE&\frz1.134\pos(542,150)}不会放过你♡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你白痴吗 你白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浴缸挺大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}值得一泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能快点出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海水的刺激性比想象中强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}头发都变粗糙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以大家才剪头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男的都剃成了光头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那我们也剪掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来帮你剪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船上有理发的工具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球粉碎了也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 我还挺会剪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}经常修自己的浏海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谜团终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}解开了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才是那个发型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准备用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧 这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.28,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn@华康特粗楷体\b0\bord0\1c&H60514C&\pos(608,464)\frx356\fry46\frz259.5}用餐时 黑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.28,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn@华康特粗楷体\b0\1c&H60514C&\3c&HEBEDE8&\frx358\fry40\pos(496,260)\frz263.3}没饭牌请找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浑身黏答答的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是你没有好好冲澡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为没时间了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马铃薯炖肉 是我们削皮的那些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有什么忘记做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃饭 洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}洗衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个还没有定好时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还不是日向你们洗澡的时候在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}负责去洗完再来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 饭都不给吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但当初因为可能会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以定好谁值日的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我记得是大家猜拳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康中特圆体\bord0\1vc(&H929A90&,&H929A90&,&H494D49&,&H494D49&)\frx350\fry340\frz9.372\pos(586,50)}洗衣间 浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an5\fn华康楷书体W5\bord0\b0\be1\1c&H85734D&\frz3.398\pos(708,268)\frx344\fry358}关于淡水的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.78,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康特粗楷体\bord0\fs25\1c&H808885&\pos(544,362)\frz2.28}综合训练期间允许使用淡水洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.77,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康特粗楷体\bord0\fs25\1c&H808885&\frz2.28\pos(588,438)}（用海水洗也行哦~）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.77,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康楷书体W7\bord0\1c&H2A3989&\pos(604,542)\frz359\frx2\fry354}努力省水喔♡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行什么行啦 结果还不是吃饱饭才洗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来得及不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定累坏了吧 比预想中忙多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是啦 明天开始也是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能努力吧 也没有选择的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉…好恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:15.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@华康俪中黑\fs22\1c&H271DB2&\3c&HA5B5BC&\frz271.1\t(0,5520,0\frz267.1)\frx4\fry6\move(1086,358,1104,374,33,5497)}上完厕所后 请将此阀门逆时针旋转冲水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:15.49,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@华康俪中黑\fs22\1c&H271DB2&\3c&HA5B5BC&\frz271.1\t(0,5520,0\frz267.1)\frx4\fry6\move(964,360,984,376,33,5497)}冲完后将阀门关紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界在旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别说话 一说话就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们晕船好严重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是之前完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晕船药也吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是药效过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟是药嘛 药效早晚会过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊 从来没坐过这么久的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以没想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日向这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃完药好好睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有就是要好好吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们大概没什么食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觉得吃了也会吐出来 所以不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是不吃饭 体力会越来越跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后会变成要靠打点滴来补充营养
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了那个地步 再怎么锻炼也没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准备用餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}佳苗小姐不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不想在南极扯后腿 就要逼自己吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全部吐光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结月也全吐光了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求求你别晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一下子就好 快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在好像停下来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是要采集海水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这也叫停…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然弓子小姐说渐渐会习惯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是根本没有习惯
